title: Jeff Zwart Pikes Peak Run, 2014 - /DRIVER'S EYE
description: Jeff Zwart in the Porsche GT3 Cup Turbo Hill Climb Special, during Pikes Peak 2014.  Soon after leaving the starting line, one of the fuel pumps begins to fail, only to get worse by the summit. Watch as Jeff battles the malfunction in real-time, at speeds upwards of 140mph.  The first time a mechanical issue appeared, even after months of testing and practice runs with the car.
tags: Pikes Peak, Porsche GT3 Cup, Hill Climb, Jeff Zwart
